commit.message:
* libgcc-std.ver: Export XFmode and TFmode versions of symbols.

From-SVN: r42605

files.patch:

+
+	* libgcc-std.ver: Export XFmode and TFmode versions of symbols.
+
 2001-05-25  Richard Henderson  <rth@redhat.com>
 
 	* config.gcc (all gnu and linux): Use t-slibgcc-elf-ver with t-linux.
